Direct the Office of the City Agriculture to submit immediately the requirements of the participating agencies for the release of the next tranche so that execution of the subject projects will resume as soon as possible and/or constant follow up from said NGAs on the release of the next tranches so that implementation of concerned projects could resume right away;

